OL,3,C'Gangland execution' of ex-prison
OL,4,Cofficer sparks demand to close law
OL,5,Cloophole
OL,7,FDemands have been made in Parliament
OL,8,Fto close "a plain gap" in the law
OL,9,Ffollowing the revenge killing of a
OL,10,Fformer prison officer.
OL,12,FThe call for the tightening up of
OL,13,Flegislation comes after career
OL,14,Fcriminal Elias Morgan gunned down
OL,15,Ffather-of-three Lenny Scott for
OL,16,Fseizing a phone from his cell years
OL,17,Fearlier.
OL,26,@pD@JOUpD@VO]
