OL,3,C'Gangland execution' of ex-prison
OL,4,Cofficer sparks demand to close law
OL,5,Cloophole
OL,7,FBecause Mr Scott had left the prison
OL,8,Fservice by then, Morgan did not face
OL,9,Fthe harshest penalty available of a
OL,10,Fwhole life order, meaning he would
OL,11,Fnever be released from jail.
OL,13,FHe was instead sentenced to serve a
OL,14,Fminimum of 45 years behind bars.
OL,16,FMorgan, of Edge Hill in Liverpool, was
OL,17,Ffound guilty of murder by an 11-person
OL,18,Fjury in August.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
