OL,3,C'Gangland execution' of ex-prison
OL,4,Cofficer sparks demand to close law
OL,5,Cloophole
OL,7,FCurrently, those who kill an on-duty
OL,8,Fprison or police officer can expect
OL,9,Fthe most severe prison sentence, where
OL,10,Fthey spend the rest of their life in
OL,11,Fjail.
OL,13,FThe Conservatives argue this should be
OL,14,Fexpanded to include offenders who
OL,15,Fmurder off-duty or former officers
OL,16,Fbecause of their job.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
