OL,3,C'Gangland execution' of ex-prison
OL,4,Cofficer sparks demand to close law
OL,5,Cloophole
OL,7,FPressing for a change to the
OL,8,FSentencing Bill currently going
OL,9,Fthrough Parliament, Tory frontbencher
OL,10,FLord Sandhurst said: "We have seen the
OL,11,Fconsequences of the existing drafting.
OL,12,FThe tragic case of former prison
OL,13,Fofficer Lenny Scott revealed the gap
OL,14,Fstarkly."
OL,16,FThe 33-year-old found a phone in
OL,17,FMorgan's cell while working at HMP
OL,18,FAltcourse in Merseyside.
OL,26,@rD@VOUvD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
