OL,3,C'Gangland execution' of ex-prison
OL,4,Cofficer sparks demand to close law
OL,5,Cloophole
OL,7,FWhen he refused a bribe to turn a
OL,8,Fblind eye and duly reported the find,
OL,9,Fwhich revealed Morgan was in a sexual
OL,10,Frelationship with a female prison
OL,11,Fofficer, the convict threatened his
OL,12,Ffamily and vowed revenge.
OL,14,FAlmost four years later, after Morgan
OL,15,Fhad served his sentence and Mr Scott
OL,16,Fhad left the Prison Service, he
OL,17,Fcarried out the threat.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
