OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F394A1764667251
OL,3,C'Gangland execution' of ex-prison
OL,4,Cofficer sparks demand to close law
OL,5,Cloophole
OL,7,FMr Scott was leaving a gym in
OL,8,FSkelmersdale, Lancashire, on February
OL,9,F8 2024, when he was shot six times by
OL,10,FMorgan.
OL,12,FLord Sandhurst said: "It was a murder
OL,13,Fdirectly and unequivocally connected
OL,14,Fto the past performance of his duties.
OL,16,F"This was a gangland execution
OL,17,Fintended to punish Lenny for doing his
OL,18,Fduty and not giving way to what had
OL,19,Fbeen asked of him, and to terrify and
OL,20,Fintimidate other prison officers into
OL,21,Fdoing gangsters' bidding in the future.
OL,26,@tD@VOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
