CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F394A1764667251
OL,3,C'Gangland execution' of ex-prison
OL,4,Cofficer sparks demand to close law
OL,5,Cloophole
OL,7,F"Because this crime did not occur in
OL,8,Fthe course of his duty but a couple of
OL,9,Fyears later, the statutory framework
OL,10,Ffailed to treat it as the kind of
OL,11,Fmurder for which Parliament provides
OL,12,Fthe highest penalty and the judge
OL,13,Ftherefore did not pass a whole-life
OL,14,Forder.
OL,16,F"This is a clear loophole in the
OL,17,Flegislation, and I look to the
OL,18,Fminister to put it right. How many
OL,19,Fmore Lennies will there be?"
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU{D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
