PN,39408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F394A1764667251
OL,3,C'Gangland execution' of ex-prison
OL,4,Cofficer sparks demand to close law
OL,5,Cloophole
OL,7,FHe added: "How many serving or former
OL,8,Fofficers walk our streets knowing that
OL,9,Fthey will remain potential targets
OL,10,Flong after they take off the uniform,
OL,11,Fand knowing that under the law as
OL,12,Fpresently interpreted, their killers
OL,13,Fmay not face the penalty that
OL,14,FParliament intended for those who
OL,15,Fattack innocent public servants?"
OL,17,FLord Sandhurst went on: "We cannot
OL,18,Fundo the tragedy that happened to
OL,19,FLenny Scott and his family, nor repair
OL,20,Fthe pain, but we can ensure that the
OL,21,Flaw is changed.
OL,26,@oD@KOUwD@aO]yD@YOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
