PN,39409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F394A1764667251
OL,3,C'Gangland execution' of ex-prison
OL,4,Cofficer sparks demand to close law
OL,5,Cloophole
OL,7,F"We can ensure that the sentencing
OL,8,Fframework recognises that the risks to
OL,9,Fofficers do not end when their shift
OL,10,Ffinishes and certainly do not
OL,11,Fdisappear when they have left the
OL,12,Fforce.
OL,14,F"When a murder is motivated and driven
OL,15,Fby the officer's service, the
OL,16,Fseriousness, risk and moral
OL,17,Fculpability are exactly the same.
OL,19,F"This is a plain gap in the
OL,20,Flegislation as currently drafted, and
OL,21,Fit must be closed immediately."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU{D@AOU}D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
