OL,3,C'Gangland execution' of ex-prison
OL,4,Cofficer sparks demand to close law
OL,5,Cloophole
OL,7,FResponding, justice minister Lord
OL,8,FTimpson said a whole-life order was
OL,9,F"normally the appropriate starting
OL,10,Fpoint" for the murder of a police or
OL,11,Fprison officer when they are on duty.
OL,13,FHe told peers: "This provision was
OL,14,Fintroduced to recognise the unique and
OL,15,Fdangerous job that police and prison
OL,16,Fofficers do on a daily basis."
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@FO]uD@POUxD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
