OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F394A1764667251
OL,3,C'Gangland execution' of ex-prison
OL,4,Cofficer sparks demand to close law
OL,5,Cloophole
OL,7,FThe minister added: "Like so many of
OL,8,Four dedicated and hard-working prison
OL,9,Fofficers, Lenny devoted his career to
OL,10,Fworking with some of this country's
OL,11,Fmost dangerous and challenging
OL,12,Foffenders.
OL,14,F"In Lenny's case, the judge considered
OL,15,Fthat this starting point did not apply
OL,16,Fas he was not a serving prison officer
OL,17,Fat the time of the murder.
OL,26,@oD@UOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
