CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F394A1764667251
OL,3,C'Gangland execution' of ex-prison
OL,4,Cofficer sparks demand to close law
OL,5,Cloophole
OL,7,F"However, the judge did impose a life
OL,8,Fsentence, with a 45-year minimum term
OL,9,Fto be served in custody, so it is
OL,10,Flikely that the perpetrator in this
OL,11,Fcase will spend the rest of his life
OL,12,Fin prison, given that he was 35 at the
OL,13,Ftime of conviction."
OL,15,FLord Timpson pointed out that the Law
OL,16,FCommission, at the request of the
OL,17,FGovernment, was currently undertaking
OL,18,Fa wholesale review of the sentencing
OL,19,Fframework for murder.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
