OL,3,C'Gangland execution' of ex-prison
OL,4,Cofficer sparks demand to close law
OL,5,Cloophole
OL,7,FHe said: "Any changes to the
OL,8,Fframework, including to whole-life
OL,9,Forders, should be considered in the
OL,10,Fcontext of this review. It would not
OL,11,Fbe appropriate to make changes before
OL,12,Fthat has finished."
OL,26,@oD@JOUtD@SO]
